---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<!-- TODO (Iulian): set up free Cloudflare Email Routing so hello@staysafeguide.com forwards to your inbox. Until then this address will not receive mail. -->
<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with Stay Safe Guide.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>Spotted a mistake, got a question, or want to suggest a guide? I would like to hear from you.</p>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@staysafeguide.com">hello@staysafeguide.com</a></p>

    <div class="callout warn">
      <p><strong>A note on safety:</strong> I can't give personalised legal or financial
      advice, and I will never ask you for your passwords, card numbers or bank details.
      Anyone contacting you claiming to be from Stay Safe Guide and asking for those things
      is not us.</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you have been scammed and need to act now, start with our guide on
    <a href="/articles/what-to-do-if-youve-been-scammed-uk/">what to do if you've been scammed</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
